Apart from the backdoor, this code seems completely ridden with bugs. E.g.<p><pre><code>    if(strstr(header, &quot;User-Agent:&quot;) != NULL)
    {
        http_request_t->0xD0 = header + strlen(&quot;User-Agent:&quot;) + strspn(header, &quot; \t&quot;);
